
# ğŸ” JavaScript Code Reviewer

A full-stack web application that reviews JavaScript code in real time using AI.  
Users can paste JavaScript code and receive:

- ğŸ§  A clear explanation of what the code does  
- âš ï¸ Identified issues and potential bugs  
- ğŸ› ï¸ A fixed/improved version of the code  
- ğŸ’¡ Suggestions for better practices and modern syntax

> Powered by **Google Gemini** on the backend and built with **React + Vite** on the frontend.

