## âœ¨ Features

- âœ… Real-time JS code analysis and feedback
- âœï¸ Natural-language explanations for any code snippet
- ğŸ§¼ Auto-suggestions for style, readability, and best practices
- ğŸ§¾ Clean diff between original and improved code
- ğŸ“‹ Copyable, ready-to-use fixed code blocks

